<title>USA: U.S. Home stake held by Greenhaven group.</title>
<headline>U.S. Home stake held by Greenhaven group.</headline>
<dateline>WASHINGTON 1997-05-14</dateline>
<text>
<p>A group led by Greenhaven Associates said Wednesday it holds a 5.09 percent stake in U.S. Home Corp or 588,750 common shares.</p>
<p>In a filing with the Securities and Exchange Commission, the group said its latest transactions include the purchase of 40,500 common shares between March 14 and May 9 at prices ranging from $25.25 to $27.25 per share.</p>
<p>U.S. Home Corp, based in Houston, Tx., is engaged in the on-site building of single-family homes.</p>
